  "instructions": [
    "heat 2 tbsp of oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "add the couscous and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "add the chickpeas, red pepper flakes, cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "add the almond milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "reduce heat to low and cook for 10-15 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "preheat the spherification bath to 180.9f.",
    "add the cooked couscous mixture to the bath and spherify the mixture.",
    "to assemble the tagine, place a banana leaf cup on a work surface and fill with 2-3 spherified couscous balls.",
    "top with chopped almonds and serve immediately.",
    "meanwhile, prepare the crumbly almond topping by mixing together the remaining almond milk, chopped almonds, and a pinch of salt. Set aside."
  ],
